docs/backtest-reports/PowerDrill Research/

# PowerDrill reference material and local audit bundles (keep on disk, not in git)
Powerdrill/
docs/audits/

# archived/stale plans (history preserved in git, not tracked going forward)
docs/plans/archive/
docs/plans/2026-03-22-*.md
docs/plans/2026-03-29-v7-implementation-plan.md

